snippet.title: Horizon Forbidden West Complete Edition - Announcement Trailer | PS5 Games
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/games/horizon-forbidden-west/

Follow the next chapter of Aloy's journey as she braves the Forbidden West – a majestic but dangerous frontier that conceals mysterious new threats - and beyond, to the ruins of Los Angeles into a treacherous archipelago.

Learn more here: https://www.playstation.com/games/horizon-forbidden-west/

©2023 Sony Interactive Entertainment Europe. Developed by Guerrilla. Horizon Forbidden West is a registered trademark or trademark of Sony Interactive Entertainment LLC.
